metadata.name: Molto Benny 2021
metadata.description:
#1  
"The first pizza box was sold, at that moment the ovens turned on, the pizza makers rolled up their sleeves and started kneading, the intention was clear 'pizza should be free for everyone'. The boxes contain a secret that will unite us for the rest of history, pizza will be history."

Molto Benny NFT is the commemorative collection of PizzaDao, born to celebrate its third anniversary in 2023, an innovative milestone of free pizza delivery worldwide in celebration of #bitcoinpizzaday every May 22 for 12 years.
